    <item>
      <title>特朗普将稳定币与美元规则挂钩，推动 Tether 和 Circle 发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-boosts-tether-circle-by-tying-stablecoins-to-dollar-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统将加密稳定币置于维护美元全球霸权的努力的最前沿，将美国政府的利益与 Tether Holdings Ltd. 和 Circle Internet Financial Ltd. 等发行人的利益牢牢结合起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-boosts-tether-circle-by-tying-stablecoins-to-dollar-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Verizon 首席执行官谈盈利、人工智能投资、移动收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/verizon-ceo-on-earnings-ai-investments-mobile-gains-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Verizon Communications Inc. 公布的第四季度财务业绩超出分析师预期，包括新增移动电话和宽带用户。董事长兼首席执行官 Hans Vestberg 在“彭博未平仓合约”上谈到增加移动和宽带用户以及新的人工智能项目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/verizon-ceo-on-earnings-ai-investments-mobile-gains-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:47:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计加元对冲关税风险的需求“巨大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/jpmorgan-sees-massive-demand-for-loonie-hedges-on-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，投资者正以历史性的速度大举对冲加元贬值，以躲避可能受到的美国关税影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/jpmorgan-sees-massive-demand-for-loonie-hedges-on-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
