      <title>关税风险缓解令欧元本周有望创一年来最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/euro-poised-for-its-best-week-in-a-year-on-easing-tariff-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者降低了对降息的预期，并押注美国贸易关税不会像之前担心的那样尽快生效，欧元本周有望创下一年多以来的最佳表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/euro-poised-for-its-best-week-in-a-year-on-easing-tariff-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷削减出口税以拯救受旱灾影响的农民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/argentina-cuts-export-taxes-to-salvage-harvest-struck-by-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷削减了主要农作物的税收，这些农作物提供了数十亿美元的出口收入，该国试图为遭受干旱和全球低迷价格困扰的农民提供救命稻草。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/argentina-cuts-export-taxes-to-salvage-harvest-struck-by-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 20:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
